name: Vol 1., Ch.4: A Drink to Forget
description: Hours go by as the girls laugh and gossip through the night. Around midnight Tiara starts to get sleepy, not being used to stay up after 10pm. “Oh, but are we just getting started!” yells Clair as she rushes through the kitchen. Minutes later she is back with a  tray of cocktails of a dark smelly liquor. “Ah Clair, you brought a drink to forget!” says Mel as she hands over the drinks.
